report with sky watch at seven.

04:44.882 --> 04:47.852
CULLY: 10 furs times 11.

04:47.885 --> 04:48.886
110.

04:48.986 --> 04:49.954
11?

04:49.987 --> 04:50.955
It was 20 in June.

04:50.988 --> 04:52.290
That was peak off season.

04:52.322 --> 04:53.457
Didn't sell.

04:53.491 --> 04:54.893
It'll all go for 11 now.

04:54.993 --> 04:57.062
Can't even take that
coon and muskrat there.

04:57.996 --> 04:59.865
How much for the beaver?

04:59.898 --> 05:01.233
Eight.

05:01.733 --> 05:05.672
♪ Now why does it matter ♪

05:05.705 --> 05:07.339
Is there anything
that didn't drop?

05:07.372 --> 05:08.975
Mink and Martin went up.

05:09.008 --> 05:10.243
Wolf is 175.

05:10.342 --> 05:11.679
Wolverine's 300.

05:12.512 --> 05:14.982
♪ But now I know ♪

05:15.015 --> 05:18.018
