23:30.557 --> 23:33.560
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

26:33.493 --> 26:36.096
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

26:42.003 --> 26:43.337
Hello.

26:46.608 --> 26:47.943
Hello.

26:48.310 --> 26:50.946
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

27:00.857 --> 27:01.858
Hey.

27:02.625 --> 27:05.461
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

28:29.254 --> 28:32.258
ANNE: What's
wrong with the food?

28:34.594 --> 28:36.229
Ate on the line.

28:49.744 --> 28:51.579
Renee says she
heard a gunshot.

28:54.582 --> 28:55.950
Thought I heard something.

28:59.755 --> 29:00.757
ANNE: And?

29:01.590 --> 29:04.160
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

29:04.260 --> 29:05.928
I was wrong.

29:07.096 --> 29:09.833
Deep in the forest
a call was sounding

29:09.932 --> 29:12.436
and as often as he
heard this call,

29:13.503 --> 29:16.106
mysteriously grilling
and learning,

29:16.139 --> 29:19.342
he felt compelled to turn
his back upon the fire

29:19.443 --> 29:21.245
and the beaming earth around it

29:21.279 --> 29:23.648
and to plunge into the forest

29:23.681 --> 29:27.018
and on and on he
knew not where or why

29:27.118 --> 29:30.088
and what did he
tender where or why.

29:30.122 --> 29:31.523
The call sounding.

29:34.694 --> 29:35.795
ANNE: Imperiously.

29:36.628 --> 29:39.499
The call sounding imperiously.

29:39.532 --> 29:42.368
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

30:20.177 --> 30:21.813
He just needs to
show himself once

30:21.846 --> 30:23.748
and it'll all be over.

30:23.848 --> 30:25.717
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

30:25.750 --> 30:26.851
I know.

30:28.586 --> 30:29.922
Tomorrow.

30:32.423 --> 30:33.691
Tomorrow.

30:33.726 --> 30:36.361
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

31:22.245 --> 31:24.783
(FLIES BUZZING)

31:27.819 --> 31:29.253
ANNE: Are you there?

31:29.286 --> 31:31.923
(FLIES BUZZING)

31:35.260 --> 31:36.428
Are you there?

31:37.495 --> 31:40.098
(FLIES BUZZING)

31:44.771 --> 31:46.138
Jo, are you there?

32:00.153 --> 32:01.488
I'm here.

32:04.994 --> 32:06.127
ANNE: Any sign yet?

32:10.331 --> 32:11.666
No.

32:14.336 --> 32:16.873
I'm gonna stay out all night
if that's what it takes.

32:18.307 --> 32:19.642
Might be out of range so.

32:21.845 --> 32:23.179
Check in tomorrow.

32:27.517 --> 32:30.021
ANNE: Promise you'll let
me know when you get it.

32:34.726 --> 32:35.827
Soon as I know.

32:38.864 --> 32:41.333
In the meantime, don't veer
too far from the cabin.

32:43.002 --> 32:45.004
You go anywhere, you
take your 22, okay?

32:46.906 --> 32:47.907
ANNE: I thought you said

32:48.007 --> 32:49.541
there was nothing
to worry about.

32:50.542 --> 32:53.179
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

32:55.849 --> 32:57.918
Just to be safe.

32:58.018 --> 32:59.419
Over and out.

32:59.519 --> 33:02.023
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

33:46.939 --> 33:48.607
Mom, I got five.

33:49.976 --> 33:52.045
That's just two off
your dad's record.

33:52.078 --> 33:53.780
Pretty soon you'll
even beat that.

33:53.813 --> 33:55.314
Yeah, I'll never beat him.

33:56.482 --> 33:58.551
Doesn't even need flat ones.

33:58.585 --> 34:00.420
He can skip any shape.

34:00.453 --> 34:03.724
(DOG BARKING)

34:03.758 --> 34:05.291
Mom, where's Tova?

34:05.325 --> 34:06.426
He can't have gone far.

34:06.459 --> 34:07.595
He was just beside me.

34:10.098 --> 34:11.431
Tova.

34:15.335 --> 34:16.437
Tova.

34:16.469 --> 34:19.108
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

34:22.444 --> 34:23.913
(WOLF GROWLING)

34:23.946 --> 34:26.648
(GIRL SCREAMING)
(OMINOUS MUSIC)

34:26.681 --> 34:28.018
Renee, get behind me.

34:28.118 --> 34:33.123
(WOLF GROWLING)
